# Our upstream ChangeLog uses the project's own format (date stanzas
# and bullet entries), not Debian-policy changelog format. debhelper
# auto-installs it as usr/share/doc/modemu2k/changelog.gz where
# lintian then tries to parse it. The format mismatch is intentional;
# the file ships as the project's documented release history.
